Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
176 Fullarton Road is a well presented fringe office building that for the first time in over 10 years has space available to lease. With side access from Swift Avenue and easily accessed via the service road, the tenancy on the ground floor is easily accessible with both ramp and stair access.

Consisting of 476 square metres with a medical fitout in place, the tenancy can be used again for medical uses or easily adapted to suit office requirements given its layout. Toilets currently being refurbished compliment the offering 

Signage opportunities are available, along with 18 on-site carparks.

A landmark building on the eastern fringe, 191 Fullarton Road, Dulwich is a prime offering in this popular commercial precinct.

Two ground floor tenancies of 130sqm and 187 sqm are available for lease with the smaller tenancy being open plan and tenancy recently refurbished including new carpets, whilst the largest tenancy is well fitted out comprising reception, boardroom, offices, meeting room, kitchen, workstations area with access to an outdoor entertaining area. 

The second floor 191sqm tenancy is also fitted out and provides outstanding natural light views of the Adelaide CBD. 

The owner is prepared to work with groups on tenancy finishes and fitouts subject to negotiation.

Best in class common facilities are provided with all toilets recently upgraded including shower.

On-site parks are available with the tenancies.
